l%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20also%20said%20it%20would%20sue%20the%20United%20States%20at%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization%20(WTO)%20and%20restrict%20the%20export%20of%20rare%20earth%20elements%20used%20in%20high-end%20medical%20and%20electronics%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20has%20been%20hit%20much%20harder%20than%20the%20USA%2C%20not%20even%20close%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20his%20post.%20%26quot%3BThey%2C%20and%20many%20other%20nations%2C%20have%20treated%20us%20unsustainably%20badly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20other%20major%20trading%20partners%20held%20back%20as%20they%20digested%20the%20unfolding%20international%20standoff%20amid%20fears%20of%20a%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Markets%20collapse%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20went%20into%20free%20fall%20Friday%2C%20following%20similar%20collapses%20in%20Asia%20and%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomists%20have%20also%20warned%20that%20the%20tariffs%20could%20dampen%20growth%20and%20fuel%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20latest%20tariffs%20have%20notable%20exclusions%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20do%20not%20stack%20onto%20recently%20imposed%2025-percent%20tariffs%20hitting%20imports%20of%20steel%2C%20aluminum%20and%20automobiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20temporarily%20spared%20are%20copper%2C%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20semiconductors%20and%20lumber%2C%20alongside%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20critical%20minerals%26quot%3B%20and%20energy%20products%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Trump%20has%20ordered%20investigations%20into%20copper%20and%20lumber%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20further%20duties%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20threatened%20to%20hit%20other%20industries%20like%20pharmaceuticals%20and%20semiconductors%20as%20well%2C%20meaning%20any%20reprieve%20might%20be%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20and%20Mexico%20are%20unaffected%20by%20the%20latest%20move%20as%20they%20already%20face%20separate%20duties%20of%20up%20to%2025%20percent%20on%20goods%20entering%20the%20United%20States%20outside%20a%20North%20America%20trade%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Retaliation%20risk%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Trump's%20staggered%20deadlines%20allow%20space%20for%20countries%20to%20negotiate%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20they%20can't%20get%20a%20reprieve%2C%20they%20are%20likely%20to%20retaliate%2C%20as%20China%20already%20has%2C%26quot%3B%20Oxford%20Economics%20warned%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEU%20trade%20chief%20Maros%20Sefcovic%20said%20the%20bloc%2C%20which%20faces%20a%2020-percent%20tariff%2C%20will%20act%20in%20%26quot%3Ba%20calm%2C%20carefully%20phased%2C%20unified%20way%26quot%3B%20and%20allow%20time%20for%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bwon't%20stand%20idly%20by.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance%20and%20Germany%20have%20said%20the%20EU%20could%20respond%20by%20imposing%20a%20tax%20on%20US%20technology%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan's%20prime%20minister%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bcalm-headed%26quot%3B%20approach%20after%20Trump%20unveiled%2024-percent%20tariffs%20on%20Japanese-made%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Trump%20said%20he%20held%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20productive%26quot%3B%20call%20with%20Vietnam's%20top%20leader%2C%20with%20imports%20from%20the%20Southeast%20Asian%20manufacturing%20hub%20facing%20extraordinary%2046-percent%20US%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20returning%20to%20the%20presidency%2C%20Trump%20has%20hit%20imports%20from%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20with%20tariffs%20over%20illegal%20immigration%20and%20fentanyl%20smuggling%2C%20and%20imposed%20an%20additional%2020-percent%20rate%20on%20goods%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECome%20April%209%2C%20the%20added%20levy%20on%20Chinese%20products%20this%20year%20will%20reach%2054%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%2025-percent%20auto%20tariffs%20also%20took%20effec