tups%20as%20%26quot%3Bmisplaced%20and%20illogical%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khandelwal%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20secretary%20general%20of%20the%20Confederation%20of%20All%20India%20Traders%20(CAIT)%2C%20said%20the%20Union%20Minister%20raised%20a%20genuine%20concern%20on%20the%20focus%20areas%20of%20Indian%20startups%2C%20and%20the%20Zepto%20CEO%20missed%20the%20essence%20of%20Mr%20Goyal's%20comments%20in%20being%20defensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClaiming%20to%20create%20jobs%20and%20pay%20taxes%20while%20burning%20foreign%20capital%20to%20dismantle%20India's%20small%20neighborhood%20kirana%20stores%20is%20not%20innovation.%20This%20approach%20is%20not%20aligned%20with%20India's%20long-term%20strategic%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20MP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%2C%20the%20Union%20Minister%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%2C%20at%20the%20'Startup%20Mahakumbh'%20event%20questioned%20Indian%20food%20delivery%20startups%20for%20turning%20unemployed%20people%20into%20cheap%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20we%20going%20to%20be%20happy%20being%20delivery%20boys%20and%20girls%3F%20Is%20that%20the%20destiny%20of%20India%3F%20This%20is%20not%20a%20startup%2C%20this%20is%20entrepreneurship.%20What%20the%20other%20side%20is%20doing%20-%20robotics%2C%20machine%20learning%2C%203D%20manufacturing%20and%20next%20generation%20factories%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Goyal%20said%20on%20Thursday%2C%20showing%20a%20slide%20titled%20'India%20vs%20China%3A%20The%20Startup%20Reality%20Check'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20admitted%20some%20criticism%20will%20come%20his%20way%20because%20of%20his%20comments%2C%20Mr%20Goyal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20objections.%20We%20have%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20learn%2C%20evolve...%20aspire%20for%20bigger%20and%20better%2C%20we%20have%20to%20be%20bolder%20and%20we%20should%20not%20shy%20of%20competition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Minister's%20comments%20sparked%20a%20huge%20debate%20online%2C%20with%20some%20CEOs%20finding%20fault%20with%20his%20assessment%20about%20startups%20in%20China%20and%20India%2C%20and%20others%20supporting%20his%20view%20about%20the%20need%20for%20Indian%20startups%20to%20take%20on%20bigger%2C%20future-oriented%2C%20and%20foundational%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20who%20pushed%20back%20at%20Mr%20Goyal's%20comment%20was%20Mr%20Palicha%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20grocery%20delivery%20app%20Zepto.%20Mr%20Palicha%20highlighted%20what%20he%20called%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3Bcontributions%26quot%3B%2C%20including%20creating%201.5%20lakh%20jobs%2C%20paying%20annual%20tax%20exceeding%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%2C%20and%20attracting%20over%20%241%20billion%20in%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20(FDI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khandelwal%20dismissed%20Mr%20Palicha's%20defence%20as%20missing%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20Union%20Minister's%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInnovation%20must%20serve%20the%20nation%2C%20not%20just%20convenience.%20We%20need%20startups%20that%20solve%20real%20problems%20and%20build%20foundational%20technologies%20to%20drive%20India's%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CAIT%20general%20secretary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khandelwal%20said%20startups%20should%20contribute%20to%20India's%20technological%20self-reliance%20and%20global%20leadership%2C%20rather%20than%20pursuing%20short-term%20commercial%20gains%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20traditional%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EBig%20allocation%20for%20Deep%20Tech%20in%20Fund%20of%20Funds%20for%20Startups.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FStartupMahakumbh%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23StartupMahakumbh%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fg9FSpvkP5n%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fg9FSpvkP5n%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Piyush%20Goyal%20(%40PiyushGoyal)%2