m%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DA1uKWw6yb_g%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarshmallow%2C%20the%20giant%20snowman%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20makes%20an%20appearance%20near%20the%20end%2C%20and%20we%20were%20wholly%20unprepared%20for%20the%20freakout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20avoided%20dark%20rides%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20did%20love%20the%20Prince%20Charming%20Regal%20Carrousel%2C%20which%20we%20figured%20would%20be%20the%20case%20since%20she%20makes%20a%20point%20to%20ride%20every%20carrousel%20she%20sees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mad%20Tea%20Party%20teacup%20ride%20was%20also%20a%20big%20hit%20%E2%80%94%20we%20were%20all%20happy%20to%20just%20sit%20in%20it%20without%20spinning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22586f9663-ffef-4155-8c52-4ce9bc67d5a5%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20toddlers%20will%20find%20Disney%20magic%20in%20the%20most%20unlikely%20of%20places%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter's%20favorite%20%26quot%3Bride%26quot%3B%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-world-skyliner-bar-crawl-what-its-like-review-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESkyliner%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20took%20us%20from%20our%20hotel%20to%20Hollywood%20Studios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20toddler%20on%20the%20skyliner%20gondola%20at%20Disney%20world%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f029fab8b41a9673fcb727%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Skyliner%20might%20have%20been%20the%20most%20magical%20part%20of%20the%20trip%20for%20my%20toddler.%3Cp%3ECaralynn%20Matassa%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20couldn't%20get%20enough%20of%20it.%20Every%20time%20we%20rode%20that%20thing%2C%20she%20hopped%20up%20on%20the%20bench%20to%20stare%20out%20the%20window%2C%20singing%20loudly%20(much%20to%20the%20amusement%20of%20other%20families%20who%20were%20shuttled%20in%20with%20us)%2C%20and%20screaming%20the%20names%20of%20all%20the%20characters%20she%20saw%20on%20the%20gondolas%20swinging%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20rides%2C%20I%20had%20measured%20my%20expectations%20for%20other%20Disney%20experiences%2C%20like%20character%20meet%20and%20greets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20anticipated%20that%20we%20would%20need%20to%20steer%20clear%20of%20most%20characters.%20We'd%20limited%20screen%20time%20until%20she%20turned%202%2C%20so%20she%20wasn't%20super%20familiar%20with%20any%20of%20them%2C%20and%20I%20worried%20she'd%20be%20freaked%20out%20seeing%20them%20(some%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever)%20in%20life-size%20form.%20We'd%20also%20had%20an%20encounter%20with%20an%20Easter%20bunny%20the%20previous%20year%20that%20gave%20me%20pause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20she%20was%20only%20a%20little%20apprehensive%20and%20warmed%20up%20to%20them%20very%20quickly.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Disney%20Jr.%20Play%20and%20Dance%2C%20she%20was%20having%20a%20dance%20party%20with%20Minnie%20Mouse%20and%20giving%20her%20hugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20couldn't%20quite%20work%20up%20the%20nerve%20to%20get%20that%20close%20to%20Goofy%2C%20who%20is%20much%20larger%20than%20Minnie%2C%20but%20all%20these%20months%20later%2C%20she's%20still%20talking%20about%20giving%20Goofy%20a%20high-five%20%26quot%3Bnext%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22meeting%20Goofy%20and%20Max%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ef0083b8b41a9673fc9d54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221462%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeeting%20Goofy%20and%20Max%20at%20a%20safe%20distance%20was%20key.%3Cp%3ECaralynn%20Matassa%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20princesses%20were%20an%20even%20bigger%20hit%2C%20and%20it%20was%20such%20a%20joy%20seeing%20her%20interact%20with%20them.%20Princess%20Elena%20was%20her%20favorite%2C%20despite%20never%20having%20watched%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20live%20music%20shows%20were%20also%20a%20great%20choice.%20On%20my%20pre-parenthood%20trips%2C%20I'd%20never%20bothered%20to%20go%20to%20them%20%E2%80%94%20who%20cares%20about%20abbreviated%20versions%20of%20Disney%20movies%20I've%20seen%20a%20trillion%20times%3F%20For%20my%20toddler%2C%20though%2C%20they%20were%20a%20major%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20under%2030%20minutes%2C%20they're%20the%20perfect%20length%20for%20short%20attention%20spans%20and%20a%20great%20primer%20for%20some%20of%20the%20movies%20she%20hadn't%20seen%20yet.%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20First%20Time%20in%20Forever%3A%20A%20Frozen%20Sing-Along%20Celebration%26quot%3B%20was%20her%20favorite%20and%20has%20sparked%20an%20intense%20Queen%20Elsa%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20safari%20ride%20at%20Animal%20Kingdom%20was%20also%20something%20I'd%20never%20done%2C%20but%20we%20prioritized%20it%20knowing%20my%20toddler's%20love%20of%20zoos.%20It%20was%20a%20major%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237596054-53a0-42ea-b78b-c3a34f423cf7%5C%22%3EThe%20fireworks%20shows%20were%20always%20a%20highlight%20of%20my%20Disney%20World%20trips%2C%20but%20they%20were%20too%20much%20for%20my%20toddler%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BFantasmic!%26quot%3B%20show%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-hollywood-studios-attractions-ranking-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHollywood%20Studios%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20my%20single%20favorite%20Disney%20experience%2C%20and%20I've%20always%20made%20a%20point%20to%20go%20multiple%20times%20during%20each%20of%20my%20past%20trips.%20However%2C%20we%20didn't%20even%20consider%20going%20with%20my%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20never%20experienced%20a%20fireworks%20show%20before%2C%20so%20to%20test%20the%20waters%2C%20we%20took%20her%20to%20%26quot%3BLuminous%3A%20The%20Symphony%20of%20Us%2C%26quot%3B%20a%2017-minute%20show%20in%20Epcot.%20We%20watched%20from%20the%20World%20Showcase%20because%20I%20figured%20that%20was%20far%20enough%20away%20from%20the%20sights%20and%20sounds%20not%20to%20be%20too%20overwhelming.%20I%20was%20extremely%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fireworks%20at%20Epcot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eef787b8b41a9673fc9bee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Epcot%20fireworks%20show%20was%20a%20big%20no.%3Cp%3ECaralynn%20Matassa%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20toddler%20was%20immediately%20freaked%20out%20by%20the%20first%20boom.%20Unfortunately%2C%20because%20the%20show%20was%20at%209%20p.m.%20(technically%20after%20the%20park%20closed)%2C%20all%20the%20stores%20and%20restaurants%20were%20inaccessible%20for%20an%20escape.%20My%20husband%20ended%20up%20taking%20refuge%20near%20a%20trash%20can%2C%20singing%20songs%20to%20keep%20her%20distracted%20until%20the%20show%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20this%20was%20a%20rookie%20mistake%3A%20We%20forgot%20to%20bring%20noise-canceling%20headphones%20for%20her.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20doubt%20she%20would%20have%20kept%20them%20on%20even%20if%20we%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20mishap%2C%20we%20knew%20to%20avoid%20%26quot%3BFantasmic!%26quot%3B%20and%20other%20fireworks%20shows%2C%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BHappily%20Ever%20After%20at%20Magic%20Kingdom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae65235b-b6f5-4b2b-97a7-6feffe0768c8%5C%22%3EMy%20toddler%20ate%20way%20more%20at%20Disney%20World%20than%20I%20expected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20home%2C%20my%20daughter%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-went-from-having-three-picky-eaters-to-none-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Every%20picky%20eater%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20convinced%20she%20can%20exist%20on%20air%20and%20the%20occasional%20Cheerio%20alone.%20It's%20a%20major%20stressor%20for%20both%20my%20husband%20and%20me%20in%20our%20day-to-day%20lives%2C%20but%20I%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20forcibly%20chill%20out%20and%20not%20worry%20about%20it%20while%20on%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20skipped%20meals%20and%20crankiness%20we%20were%20anticipating%2C%20we%20were%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20her%20slightly%20more%20adventurous%20appetite%20at%20Disney%20World.%20Now%2C%20she%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20exactly%20angling%20to%20chow%20down%20on%20a%20turkey%20leg%2C%20but%20it%20was%20better%20than%20I%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22pastry%20basket%20at%20Cinderella's%20Royal%20Table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eef7c369253ccddf9b354e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20all%20loved%20the%20pastry%20selection%20at%20Cinderella's%20Royal%20Table.%3Cp%3ECaralynn%20Matassa%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20favorites%20included%20the%20Mickey-shaped%20blueberry%20muffins%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcinderellas-royal-table-disney-world-review-worth-it-photos-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECinderella's%20Royal%20Table%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20pizza%20at%20Connections%20Cafe%2C%20and%20clementines%20and%20french%20fries%20wherever%20we%20could%20find%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20win%2C%20though%2C%20was%20the%20Nemo%20Fin-tastic%20Cake%20at%20Coral%20Reef%2C%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20restaurants%20in%20Disney%20World.%20She's%20usually%20not%20a%20sweets%20girl%20(much%20to%20my%20distress%2C%20as%20a%20big%20Dole%20Whip%20fan)%20and%20the%20cake%20was%20so%20cute%20she%20wasn't%20initially%20sure%20whether%20it%20was%20even%20edible.%20Once%20she%20took%20the%20first%20bite%2C%20though%2C%20she%20couldn't%20get%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20bonus%20is%20that%20kids%20under%203%20eat%20free%20at%20all-you-care-to-enjoy%20Disney%20restaurants.%20%3Ca%20