%20exhausted%20from%20the%20weekly%20trips%2C%20so%20I%20handed%20him%20the%20grocery%20list%20%E2%80%94%20half%20expecting%20him%20to%20come%20back%20overwhelmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20month%2C%20our%20grocery%20bill%20dropped%20to%20%241%2C511.%20I%20figured%20he%20was%20just%20cutting%20corners%20to%20prove%20he%20could%20spend%20less.%20But%20the%20following%20month%3F%20%241%2C555.%20Our%20pantry%20was%20full%2C%20our%20kids%20were%20happy%2C%20and%20we%20were%20spending%20around%20%24400%20less%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20admit%3A%20maybe%20my%20husband%20was%20onto%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210db9c48-55be-40f8-82dc-40bc61297fee%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20started%20by%20taking%20his%20time%20in%20the%20store%20to%20consider%20all%20the%20options%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20curious%20about%20his%20method%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20are%20you%20doing%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20his%20first%20grocery%20shopping%20trip%20took%20almost%20two%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20because%20he%20couldn't%20find%20anything.%20While%20I%20was%20home%20imagining%20him%20wandering%20lost%20in%20the%20aisles%2C%20he%20was%20carefully%20reading%20ads%20(the%20ones%20I%20would%20have%20tossed%20aside)%20and%20checking%20prices%20on%20every%20single%20item.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEver%20the%20engineer%2C%20my%20husband%20pulled%20out%20his%20phone%20to%20show%20me%20some%20of%20the%20side-by-side%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-vs-target-grocery-shopping-which-is-better-review-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprice%20comparisons%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20made.%20I%20was%20beyond%20surprised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295f8b43f-9972-45ea-b65e-48adb3eaf3a3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20husband%20made%20some%20big%20money-saving%20switches%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20go%20through%20ketchup%20like%20water.%20I%20had%20been%20buying%20Heinz%20at%20%244.48%20for%20years%20without%20thinking%20twice.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-walmart-brand-cream-cheese-highlights-the-problem-with-the-us-economy-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGreat%20Value%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E%20my%20husband%20chose%20is%20just%20%241.92%20for%20the%20same%20size%20bottle%2C%20and%20it%20tastes%20exactly%20the%20same%2C%20saving%20us%20%242.56%20every%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Heinz%20ketchup%20next%20to%20cheaper%20generic%20ketchup%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eaf9a8b8b41a9673fc3637%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20generic%20brand%20of%20ketchup%20is%20cheaper.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Amy%20Braun%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20ranch%20savings%20may%20be%20one%20of%20our%20biggest.%20Switching%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-brand-has-best-ranch-dressing-grocery-store-ranking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHidden%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20%246.97%20to%20Great%20Value%20at%20%243.54%20saves%20us%20%243.43%20per%20bottle%2C%20and%20no%20one%20can%20even%20tell%20the%20difference.%20We%20use%20it%20for%20everything%20from%20salads%20to%20dipping%20vegetables%2C%20so%20these%20savings%20add%20up%20quickly.%20We%20even%20did%20a%20blind%20taste%20test%20with%20our%20pickiest%20eater%2C%20and%20he%20liked%20the%20generic%20brand%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cereal%20aisle%20turned%20out%20to%20have%20big%20savings%2C%20too.%20Name-brand%20Rice%20Krispies%20were%20costing%20us%20%243.98%20per%20box%2C%20but%20Great%20Value%20Rice%20Crisps%20are%20only%20%241.97.%20This%20cut%20our%20cost%20in%20half%20while%20keeping%20breakfast%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20kids'%20school%20snacks%2C%20I%20used%20to%20buy%20the%20individually%20packaged%20Goldfish%20for%20%249.76%20out%20of%20convenience.%20My%20husband%20started%20buying%20the%20bulk%20carton%20for%20%247.79%20which%20saves%20us%20almost%20%242.00%20for%20even%20more%20crackers.%20For%20what%20we%20are%20saving%2C%20I%20don't%20mind%20taking%20the%20extra%20minute%20to%20put%20the%20Goldfish%20into%20individual%20baggies%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthy-eating-at-school-college-kids-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschool%20snacks%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223679%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hidden%20valley%20ranch%20next%20to%20generic%20brand%20ranch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eafa17b8b41a9673fc3654%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222760%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20generic%20brand%20of%20ranch%20is%20cheaper.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Amy%20Braun%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20about%20switching%20to%20store%20brands%20or%20buying%20in%20bulk.%20Even%20with%20name-brand%20things%20we%20love%2C%20my%20husband%20finds%20a%20way%20to%20save%20money.%20For%20example%2C%20with%20our%20coffee%2C%20instead%20of%20paying%20%2431.08%20at%20Walmart%20for%20three%20pounds%2C%20he%20gets%20it%20directly%20from%20Dunkin%20on%20his%20way%20home%20for%20%2426.21.%20That's%20saving%20%244.87%20just%20by%20changing%20where%20we%20buy%20it.%20It's%20the%20exact%20same%20amount%2C%20but%20almost%20%245.00%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226b4ee15f-8412-4449-95d8-5fa21a80531b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe're%20happier%20and%20saving%20money%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20unexpected%20benefits%20beyond%20just%20saving%20money.%20I%20no%20longer%20dread%20those%20weekly%20grocery%20trips%20because%20I'm%20not%20making%20them%20anymore.%20Since%20my%20husband%20actually%20sticks%20to%20the%20grocery%20list%20(unlike%20me%20and%20my%20impulse%20purchases)%2C%20we're%20wasting%20less%20food.%3C%2Fp%3