ider.com%2F67ed5a3c63d72727e198f59f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20train%20from%20the%20platform.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20boarded%20the%20train%20and%20walked%20to%20my%20sleeper%20cabin%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20car%2C%20right%20next%20to%20one%20of%20the%20two%20bathrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20blue%20train%20was%20dimly%20lit%2C%20dated%2C%20and%20had%20a%20stale%20odor.%20My%20room%20was%20the%20size%20of%20a%20large%20closet%2C%20but%20I%20had%20it%20all%20to%20myself%2C%20and%20it%20felt%20surprisingly%20cozy.%20I%20hung%20my%20coat%20and%20took%20a%20few%20minutes%20to%20get%20settled%20and%20organize%20my%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20room%20had%20a%20three-bed%20bunk%2C%20with%20the%20middle%20bed%20swung%20down%20to%20act%20as%20a%20backrest%20for%20the%20bottom%20bed%2C%20where%20one%20would%20sit%20(eventually%2C%20I%20raised%20the%20middle%20bed%20to%20sleep%20on).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20only%20window%2C%20there%20were%20some%20hangers%2C%20a%20small%20fold-down%20chair%2C%20a%20ladder%2C%20a%20storage%20rack%2C%20and%20a%20small%20desk%20with%20a%20mirror%20that%20opened%20and%20hosted%20an%20electrical%20outlet.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20spartan%20space%2C%20certainly%20not%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-biden-ukraine-kyiv-visit-railway-service-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20luxury%20train%3C%2Fa%3E%20Western%20leaders%20have%20used%20to%20travel%20into%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20past%2C%20but%20it%20was%20sufficient%20for%20what%20I%20needed%20it%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESleeper%20cars%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%20cabin%20for%20the%20next%2016%20hours.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ed7b7369253ccddf9b0afb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20cabin%20for%20the%20next%2016%20hours.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20train%20cabin%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20other%20view%20of%20my%20cabin%2C%20sitting%20by%20the%20window.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ed7bb763d72727e198fd26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20other%20view%20of%20my%20cabin.%20There%20was%20a%20desk%20in%20the%20corner%2C%20so%20I%20could%20do%20a%20little%20work.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cabin%20was%20equipped%20with%20three%20plastic%20packets%20containing%20sheets%2C%20a%20pillowcase%2C%20and%20a%20towel.%20What%20looked%20like%20sleeping%20pads%20and%20pillows%20were%20on%20the%20top%20bunk%2C%20and%20blankets%20were%20on%20a%20storage%20rack.%20(I%20didn't%20end%20up%20using%20any%20of%20them.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cabin%20also%20came%20stocked%20with%20two%20bottles%20of%20water%2C%20but%20I'd%20packed%20my%20own%2C%20along%20with%20some%20Pringles%2C%20biscuits%2C%20and%20Mentos%20to%20hold%20me%20over%20until%20I%20got%20to%20Kyiv.%20I%20figured%20there%20was%20a%20good%20chance%20I'd%20be%20up%20all%20night%20and%20get%20hungry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJust%20me%20and%20my%20bags%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22I%20had%20my%20backpack%2C%20camera%20bag%2C%20suitcase%2C%20and%20two%20duffle%20bags%20with%20gear%20and%20other%20supplies.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ed7c1469253ccddf9b0b1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20had%20my%20backpack%2C%20camera%20bag%2C%20suitcase%2C%20and%20two%20duffle%20bags%20with%20gear%20and%20other%20supplies.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEverything%20I%20needed%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20top%20bunk%20had%20some%20extra%20stuff%20for%20sleeping.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ed7c9469253ccddf9b0b3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20top%20bunk%20had%20some%20extra%20stuff%20for%20sleeping.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20train%20pulled%20away%20from%20the%20station%20shortly%20after%20its%20scheduled%20departure%20time.%20By%20this%20point%2C%20it%20was%20dark%20outside.%20Around%2015%20minutes%20later%2C%20someone%20came%20by%20to%20check%20my%20tickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20Google%20Translate%20to%20communicate%20with%20him%2C%20and%20he%20tried%20to%20speak%20English%20at%20one%20point.%20The%20only%20word%20I%20could%20really%20make%20out%20from%20the%20exchange%20was%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-troops-another-gun-if-run-out-of-us-bullets-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20reporting%20trip%20came%20right%20after%20a%20contentious%20White%20House%20meeting%20between%20the%20US%20president%20and%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20and%20as%20the%20Trump%20administration%20was%20pressuring%20Ukraine%20to%20make%20unfavorable%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20train%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20traveling%20fast%2C%20though%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20our%20speed%20was.%20They%20may%20have%20said%20something%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20speak%20Ukrainian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20across%20Poland%20was%20bumpy%20and%20loud.%20During%20the%20first%20three%20hours%20of%20my%20ride%2C%20I%20prepped%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzelenskyy-advisor-patriots-weapon-concern-over-trump-aid-cuts-ukraine-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterviews