https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC3652364%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20in%20the%20early%201980s%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20decade%20or%20so%20later%2C%20it%20went%20mainstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20really%20started%20seeing%20them%20gain%20popularity%2C%20or%20in%20the%20very%20least%20the%20general%20public%20becoming%20more%20aware%20of%20them%2C%20in%20the%20late%201990s%20when%20many%20actors%20and%20actresses%20in%20Hollywood%20were%20opting%20for%20large%2C%20white%2C%20more%20obvious%20veneers%2C%26quot%3B%20Los%20Angeles-based%20cosmetic%20dentist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdrjonmarashi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Jon%20Marashi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20clients%20include%20Ryan%20Seacrest%2C%20Kate%20Hudson%2C%20and%20Ben%20Affleck%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr.%20Jon%20Marashi%2C%20a%20cosmetic%20dentist%20to%20the%20stars%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f03491b8b41a9673fcb9a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr.%20Jon%20Marashi%2C%20a%20cosmetic%20dentist%20to%20the%20stars%2C%20says%20demand%20is%20soaring%20for%20no-prep%20veneers%3Cp%3EAntar%20Hanif%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20veneers%20first%20emerged%2C%20the%20procedure%20was%20less%20invasive%2C%20since%20the%20material%20of%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20feldspathic%20porcelain%20%E2%80%94%20was%20very%20thin%20and%20could%20fit%20neatly%20on%20most%20teeth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20stronger%20materials%20have%20emerged%20that%20are%20better%20at%20covering%20up%20imperfections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20materials%2C%20such%20as%20zirconia%20or%20lithium%20disilicate%2C%20are%20now%20the%20standard.%20They're%20up%20to%2050%25%20thicker%2C%20making%20them%20less%20fragile%20and%20easier%20to%20work%20with%20for%20both%20veneers%20(co