jpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Dolomites%20from%20the%20reporter's%20balcony.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-five-star-hotels-most-surprising-things-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive-star%20hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%20sits%205%2C905%20meters%20above%20sea%20level%20near%20the%20Italian%20town%20of%20Brixen.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201912%2C%20the%20property%20was%20originally%20planned%20to%20be%20a%20sanatorium%20built%20by%20the%20Austrian%20monarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20area's%20fresh%20spring%20water%2C%20mountain%20air%2C%20and%20nature%20were%20thought%20to%20provide%20an%20ideal%20environment%20for%20healing.%20Construction%20started%2C%20but%20the%20plans%20were%20never%20finished%20as%20war%20sprung%20across%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202000%2C%20hotelier%20Alois%20Hinteregger%20discovered%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexploring-abandoned-rock-a-hoola-water-park-california-desert-photos-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabandoned%20building%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20his%20family%20purchased%20and%20opened%20as%20a%20hotel%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20later%2C%20Alois'%20son%20Stefan%20and%20his%20partner%2C%20Teresa%20Unterthiner%2C%20expanded%20the%20property%20and%20transformed%20it%20into%20the%20five-star%20retreat%20it%20is%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThree%20towers%20of%20suites%20and%20a%20private%20villa%20complete%20the%20resort.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20one%20of%20the%20property's%20three%20towers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eea90a69253ccddf9b2539%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20one%20of%20the%20property's%20three%20towers.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%20and%20I%20arrived%20at%20the%20property%20at%20night.%20We%20drove%20up%20the%20winding%20Plose%20Mountain%2C%20and%20the%20lights%20from%20the%20nearby%20town%20slowly%20disappeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20at%20night%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20Forestis%20was%20a%20grand%20property.%20Three%20towers%20stretch%20toward%20the%20sky%2C%20home%20to%2040%20suites%20and%20two%20penthouses.%20Adjoining%20the%20towers%20is%20a%20historic%20building%20with%20suites%2C%20hotel%20rooms%2C%20a%20restaurant%2C%20a%20bar%2C%20and%20a%20spa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20sanatorium%20never%20operated%20as%20planned%2C%20one%20completed%20building%20did%20serve%20as%20a%20doctor's%20residence%20in%20the%20early%2020th%20century.%20That%20building%20has%20been%20remodeled%20and%20restored%20to%20a%20private%20villa%20with%20a%20spa%20and%20garden%20for%2010%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERates%20at%20the%20five-star%20property%20start%20at%20%24865%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20time%20of%20year%2C%20and%20include%20breakfast%20for%20two.%20Business%20Insider%20received%20a%20media%20rate%20for%20the%20three-night%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPiney%20references%20are%20across%20the%20entire%20property.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20the%20FORESTIS%20property.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eeaa4163d72727e1991811%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20the%20property.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20rooms%20with%20spruce-paneled%20walls%20to%20a%20spa%20using%20mountain%20pine%20and%20Swiss%20stone%20pine%20scents%2C%20Forestis%20is%20consistent%20in%20its%20theme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resort's%20goal%20is%20to%20connect%20guests%20with%20the%20four%20elements%2C%20and%20for%20three%20days%2C%20it%20was%20impossible%20to%20forget%20I%20was%20surrounded%20by%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESuites%20feature%20floor-to-ceiling%20glass%20windows%20that%20frame%20the%20mountains.%20Meanwhile%2C%20each%20suite's%20walls%2C%20floors%2C%20and%20ceiling%20are%20paneled%20in%20spruce.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20suite.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eea8dc69253ccddf9b2530%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reporter's%20tower%20suite.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20stepped%20into%20my%20tower%20suite%2C%20the%20forest%20theme%20continued.%20Every%20inch%20of%20the%20room%20was%20covered%20in%20spruce%20wood%2C%20besides%20one%20wall%20dedicated%20to%20glass%20windows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20king-sized%20bed%20filled%20one%20corner%20facing%20the%20suite's%20floor-to-ceiling%20windows%2C%20and%20across%20the%20room%20was%20an%20L-shaped%20seating%20area.%20At%20the%20front%20of%20the%20room%20was%20a%20balcony%20with%20a%20daybed%20big%20enough%20for%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToward%20the%20entrance%20to%20the%20room%20was%20a%20large%20closet%20area%20and%20a%20stone-inspired%20bathroom%20with%20a%20double%20vanity%2C%20shower%2C%20and%20tub.%20Here%2C%20rock%20had%20been%20ground%20into%20plaster%20and%20covered%20the%20bathroom%20walls%20%E2%80%94%20an%20element%20I%20spotted%20across%20the%20resort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20cabinet%20held%20complimentary%20drinks%20and%20snacks%3B%20a%20new%20treat%2C%20such%20as%20truffles%20and%20chocolates%2C%20arrived%20just%20before%20bedtime%20each%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20room's%20design%20was%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20there%20was%20no%20artwork%20or%20decor.%20Couch%20cushions%20and%20bed%20sheets%20were%20in%20grays%20and%20whites%2C%20and%20it%20seemed%20like%20all%20focus%20was%20directed%20toward%20the%20nearby%20Dolomites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhile%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20leave%20the%20breathtaking%20room%2C%20the%20resort's%20highlight%20was%20the%20spa%20and%20pool.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20pools%20at%20FORESTIS.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eea9cdb8b41a9673fc8c1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20pools.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20waking%20up%20to%20the%20striking%20mountain%20views%2C%20my%20friend%20and%20I%20considered%20never%20leaving%20the%20suite.%20We%20could%20call%20room%20service%20when%20hungry%20and%20spend%20the%20day%20admiring%20the%20mountains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20tempting%2C%20but%20we%20headed%20downstairs%20to%20explore%20the%20spa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20considered%20never%20leaving%20the%20suite%2C%20exiting%20the%20spa%20was%20even%20more%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20the%2021%2C500-square-foot%20spa%20was%20the%20most%20impressive%20pool%20I've%20ever%20seen.%20Unsurprisingly%2C%20the%20pool%20had%20views%20of%20the%20Dolomites.%20Half%20of%20it%20was%20indoors%2C%20and%20the%20other%20was%20outdoors.%20Guests%20could%20swim%20between%20the%20two%20through%20sliding%20glass%20doors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20also%20had%20loungers%2C%20daybeds%2C%20a%20water%20station%20with%20small%20snacks%2C%20a%20sauna%2C%20and%20a%20steam%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20hallway%20led%20to%20another%20wing%20of%20the%20spa%2C%20which%20had%20two%20more%20indoor%20saunas%2C%20one%20at%20185%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20and%20another%20at%20158%20degrees.%20There%20was%20a%20cold%20plunge%2C%20a%20silent%20room%20with%20a%20fireplace%2C%20and%20a%20tea%20lounge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20door%20led%20outdoors%20to%20the%20fifth%20sauna%2C%20which%20was%20tucked%20inside%20a%20traditional%20South%20Tyrolean%20wooden%20house%2C%20and%20a%20second%20outdoor%20cold%20plunge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20access%20to%20these%20amenities%20is%20included%20in%20the%20stay%2C%20the%20property's%20spa%20also%20offers%20treatments%20like%20massages%2C%20facials%2C%20scrubs%2C%20and%20manicures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHere%2C%20guests%20discover%20the%20magic%20of%20saunas%20and%20cold%20plunging.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20images%20of%20the%20cold%20plunge%20and%20sauna%20at%20FORESTIS.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eeaa0c69253ccddf9b2571%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESide-by-side%20images%20of%20the%20cold%20plunge%20and%20sauna.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20spa%20offerings%2C%20Forestis%20has%20a%20daily%20calendar%20of%20activities%20for%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%20and%20I%20debated%20between%20meditation%20sessions%20and%20guided%20hikes.%20Ultimately%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20join%20the%20daily%20complimentary%20sauna%20ritual.%20Celtic%20practices%20inspire%20Forestis'%20spa%2C%20and%20perhaps%20this%20one%20encapsulated%20that%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaro%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20spa%20team%2C%20led%20the%20ritual.%20We%20stepped%20inside%20the%20hot%20sauna%20with%20two%20other%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20steam%20rose%20from%20the%20rocks%2C%20Saro%20turned%20on%20powerful%20instrumental%20music%2C%20flicked%20open%20a%20large%20fan%2C%20and%20danced%20for%20the%20next%2015%20minutes.%20New%20essential%20oils%20were%20thrown%20onto%20the%20rocks%20every%20five%20minutes%2C%20enveloping%20the%20sauna%20in%20a%20new%20(typically%20pine)%20scent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20focused%20on%20breathing%20as%20we%20were%20hit%20with%20waves%20of%20heat.%20Meditating%20through%20the%20hot%20air%20was%20relaxing%2C%20incred