0Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20highly%20deserves%20this%20honour%3B%20that%20is%20what%20we%20firmly%20believe%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Anura%20Kumara%20Dissanayake%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReceiving%20the%20award%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-in-sri-lanka-lankas-big-gesture-for-pm-modi-a-grand-welcome-that-sets-new-precedent-8091848%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPM%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmatter%20of%20pride%26quot%3B%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20to%20be%20honoured%20with%20the%20Sri%20Lanka%20Mitra%20Vibhushan%20award%20by%20President%20Anura%20Kumara%20Dissanayake%20-%20it's%20not%20an%20honour%20to%20me%20but%20to%20140%20crore%20Indians.%20It%20shows%20the%20historical%20relation%20and%20deep%20friendship%20between%20the%20people%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20India%2C%20and%20for%20this%2C%20I%20thank%20the%20president%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20and%20the%20people%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22tl%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Colombo%20%7C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20receives%20Mithra%20Vibhushana%20award%20from%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%20Anura%20Kumara%20Dissanayake%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn(Source%20-%20ANI%2FDD)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9xvngn9q00%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F9xvngn9q00%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1908416101114847509%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%205%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20award%20marks%20the%2022nd%20international%20recognition%20bestowed%20on%20PM%20Modi%20by%20a%20foreign%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Mithra%20Vibhushana'%20medal%20is%20specially%20instituted%20to%20recognise%20extraordinary%20global%20friendships%20and%20reflect%20the%20depth%20and%20warmth%20of%20India-Sri%20Lanka%20relations.%20The%20'Dharma%20Chakra'%20on%20it%20represents%20the%20shared%20Buddhist%20heritage%20that%20has%20shaped%20the%20cultural%20traditions%20of%20both%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Pun%20Kalasa'%20-%20a%20ceremonial%20pot%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20medal%20is%20adorned%20with%20sheaves%20of%20rice%2C%20signifying%20prosperity%20and%20renewal.%20This%20is%20surrounded%20by%20'Navrathna'%20-%20nine%20precious%20gems%20-%20symbolising%20the%20enduring%20friendship%20between%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%20The%20gems%20are%20depicted%20within%20a%20globe%20encircled%20by%20lotus%20petals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sun%20and%20Moon%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20medal%20represent%20the%20timeless%20nature%20of%20the%20relationship%2C%20stretching%20from%20ancient%20history%20into%20the%20infinite%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20these%20elements%20capture%20the%20deep%20cultural%20and%20spiritual%20connection%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20highest%20civilian%20award%20of%20the%20island%20nation%20was%20introduced%20in%202008%20by%20former%20President%20Mahinda%20Rajapaksa.%20Only%20three%20other%20leaders%2C%20apart%20from%20PM%20Modi%2C%20have%20been%20conferred%20with%20the%20award%20-%20Former%20President%20of%20Maldives%20Maumoon%20Abdul%20Gayoom%2C%20President%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Palestine%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%2C%20and%20Palestinian%20leader%20Yasser%20Arafat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%20Modi%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20arrived%20in%20Colombo%20on%20Friday%20where%20he%20received%20a%20grand%20ceremonial%20welcome%20at%20the%20historic%20Independence%20Square%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20capital.%20This%20was%20perhaps%20the%20first%20such%20honour%20given%20to%20a%20foreign%20leader.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20his%20arrival%2C%20PM%20Modi%20and%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%20held%20bilateral%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20signed%20several%20key%20pacts%2C%20including%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-sri-lanka-sign-key-defence-pact-after-pm-narendra-modi-president-dissanayakas-meet-8092446%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emajor%20defence%20cooperation%20pact%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20the%20first%20time%20and%20one%20to%20develop%20Trincomalee%20as%20an%20energy%20hub.%20Another%20agreement%20was%20signed%20to%20provide%20India's%20multi-sectoral%20grant%20assistance%20to%20the%20eastern%20region%20of%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20also%20virtually%20inaugurated%20several%20key%20bilateral%20projects%2C%20including%20the%20Sampur%20Solar%20Power%20Project%20and%20a%20Temperature-Controlled%20Agriculture%20Warehouse%20in%20Dambulla.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743839340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fsrmb5o5s_modi-award_625x300_05_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-gets-sri-lankas-highest-civilian-award-mithra-vibhushana-matter-of-pride-8092506%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20'Mithra%20Vibhushana'%20medal%20is%20specially%20instituted%20to%20recognise%20extraordinary%20global%20friendships%20and%20reflect%20the%20depth%20and%20warmth%20of%20India-Sri%20Lanka%20relations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-gets-sri-lankas-highest-civilian-award-mithra-vibhushana-matter-of-pride-8092506%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Barack%20Obama%20admits%20US%20presidency%20term%20affected%20relationship%20with%20Michelle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publ