%2F04%2FUger-side-reverse_11zon-1-1743519204-300x195.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FUger-side-reverse_11zon-1-1743519204-500x325.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FUger-side-reverse_11zon-1-1743519204-768x498.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FUger-side-reverse_11zon-1-1743519204-1536x997.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FUger-side-reverse_11zon-1-1743519204-2048x1329.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FUger-side-reverse_11zon-1-1743519204-1200x779.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FUger-side-reverse_11zon-1-1743519204-150x97.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-417324%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222310%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Uger%20kit%20includes%20cloth%20pads%20and%20absorbent%20inserts%20that%20can%20be%20fixed%20with%20straps%20%E2%80%94%20a%20flexible%2C%20low-waste%20alternative%20to%20disposable%20pads%2C%20priced%20at%20Rs%20180%20for%20a%203-month%20supply.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pad%20is%20not%20leak-proof%20%E2%80%94%20intentionally%20so.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20took%20a%20conscious%20decision%20not%20to%20coat%20it%20with%20polymers%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProject%20Uger%20garnered%20national%20and%20international%20recognition%20and%20is%20now%20being%20replicated%20across%20the%20country.%20In%20an%20unusual%20but%20powerful%20move%2C%20Lakshmi%20chose%20not%20to%20copyright%20the%20Uger%20design.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20Self-Help%20Groups%20(SHGs)%20have%20copied%20the%20pad.%20We%20helped%20four%20SHGs%20in%20Northeast%20India%20set%20up%20units%20to%20make%20it.%20The%20Aditya%20Birla%20Group%20runs%20a%20unit%20in%20Jalna%2C%20Maharashtra.%20Mitu%20Foundation%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20making%20it%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pad%20was%20intentionally%20kept%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9CCopy%20Left%E2%80%9D%20space%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20allowed%20anyone%20to%20replicate%20the%20design%20without%20legal%20restriction.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20a%20conscious%20choice%20to%20ensure%20the%20product%20reached%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible%2C%20without%20commercial%20barriers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lakshmi%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202876px)%20100vw%2C%202876px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FFolded-pads_11zon-1743519258.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222876%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reusable%20cotton%20pads%20from%20Project%20Uger%20%E2%80%94%20eco-friendly%2C%20affordable%2C%20and%20designed%20to%20be%20stitched%20and%20sold%20by%20rural%20women.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FFolded-pads_11zon-1743519258.jpg%202876w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FFolded-pads_11zon-1743519258-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FFolded-pads_11zon-1743519258-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FFolded-pads_11zon-1743519258-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FFolded-pads_11zon-1743519258-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FFolded-pads_11zon-1743519258-2048x1536.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FFolded-pads_11zon-1743519258-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FFolded-pads_11zon-1743519258-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FFolded-pads_11zon-1743519258-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FFolded-pads_11zon-1743519258-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FFolded-pads_11zon-1743519258-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FFolded-pads_11zon-1743519258-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-417326%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222157%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EReusable%20cotton%20pads%20from%20Project%20Uger%20%E2%80%94%20eco-friendly%2C%20affordable%2C%20and%20designed%20to%20be%20stitched%20and%20sold%20by%20rural%20women.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20centre%20operated%20through%20a%20decentralised%20model.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20robust%20production.%20We%20had%2010%20women%20working%20from%20home.%20They%20would%20come%20to%20the%20centre%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20materials%2C%20stitch%20the%20pads%20at%20home%20and%20come%20back%20to%20deliver%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20time%2C%20as%20more%20players%20entered%20the%20market%20and%20disposable%20pads%20flooded%20rural%20areas%2C%20production%20dwindled.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sadness%20for%20me%20comes%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20free%20disposable%20pads%20were%20supplied%20in%20schools%20across%20Rajasthan.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20I%20understand%20it%20is%20a%20rights%20and%20convenience%20issue.%20But%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20is%20a%20huge%20environmental%20issue.%20In%20rural%20areas%2C%20there%20is%20no%20proper%20disposal%20system.%20They%20just%20lie%20around%20and%20end%20up%20in%20landfills.%20Even%20so-called%20compostable%20pads%20are%20not%20fully%20compostable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20period%20work%20really%20takes